name: preLoggingGLDistributionCurrentYear

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged in to 'GL Distribution Voucher Match' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Pre-Registration,GL Distribution/Voucher Match}

testSteps.description: Then the 'GL Distribution' page and its contents should show up
When I click the 'GL Distribution' button from the first search result
Then the 'GL Distribution' form should show up
When I fill up 'GL Distribution' table form Account Number: '937000', Line Description: 'TEST GL Distribution Current Month', Cost Center: 'BAM5000', AOE: 'KAB', Line Ref: 'TEST'
Then the 'GL Distribution Successful Created' modal should show up
When i click on modal review button
When I click on 'Show Posted Batches' checkbox
Then the 'Voucher Entry Review' page and its contents should show up
When I select the first voucher entry
When I click on 'View Entries' button
Then the 'Voucher Entry' modal should show up
When I click on modal 'Close' button

title: Pre logging GL distribution current year
